@startuml
title 点云渲染管线（复杂度 O(n³)）

actor 质检员 as user
participant "Three.js 前端" as front
participant "Gateway" as gw
participant "zrws-process" as svc
database "MySQL" as db
database "Redis" as cache

== 点云加载与渲染 ==
user -> front: 打开点云视图
front -> gw: GET /api/v1/pointcloud/{id}/tiles
gw -> svc: 转发
svc -> db: [SQL] SELECT t_point_cloud WHERE mission_id=1024
svc -> svc: Potree 八叉树分片
svc --> gw: 分片索引 JSON
gw --> front: tile manifest
front -> front: Three.js + Potree-core 渐进加载
front -> front: 百万点云 @ ≥30FPS

== 实时交互 ==
user -> front: 旋转/缩放/测量
front -> front: GPU 拾取 + 距离计算
front -> svc: STOMP /queue/pointcloud.annotations
svc -> db: [SQL] INSERT t_annotation

== 异常流程 ==
alt 显存不足
    front -> front: 降级 LOD 策略
    front -> user: 自动切换低精度
else 分片加载超时
    front -> svc: 重试 3 次
    front -> user: 加载失败，检查网络
end

@enduml
